urdu transliteration text:
Jisne larte huwe abbas ko ranme dekhausko yaad aaye yadullah ki talwaar ke haath
Whoever saw Abbas fighting in the battlefield,
@HujjatELC

Mere Asgher hai kahaan maa ne tadapker poochaaaye khali jo nazar sayyade abraar ke haath
When she saw the Imam’s hands empty
@HujjatELC
